description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;An exciting development opportunity has arisen for two permanent Band 6 Operational Support Managers and one 12 month fixed term Band 6 Operational Support Manager within the Medicine Clinical Services Group at the Royal Glamorgan Hospital. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are looking for three well-motivated, enthusiastic individuals to join our team and the successful applicants will be responsible for the delivery of high quality, safe, effective and innovative services within the Medicine Clinical Services Group in line with national and locally agreed standards. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and/or English speakers are equally welcome to apply. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing Date: 12/11/2020 &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Amanda Powell&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Clinical Service Group Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: Amanda.J.Powell2@wales.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number: 01443 443443 ext 74128 &lt;/p&gt;
